# Quote API Key for TheQuote API – get your key from https://thequoteapi.com/
# Next.js only exposes env vars prefixed with NEXT_PUBLIC_ to the browser.
# This is used client-side when fetching random quotes (see src/lib/api/quote.ts).
# (If migrating from Vite: the old var was VITE_QUOTE_API_KEY; use this name in Next.js.)
NEXT_PUBLIC_QUOTE_API_KEY=your-api-key-here
